Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.38,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直诉说着的自我风格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:36.47,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但也搞不太懂究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:43.72,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迷失在露出扭曲笑容和叹息的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:45.60,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:50.35,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在"这个世界"印象的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:54.69,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有着不同的世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:23:00.28,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要找出所有重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.03,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}亲眼地确认
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:06.41,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please Please Me 请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:10.50,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要伸出双手拥抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:14.46,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let me free 请露出笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.63,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}答案一直都在镜像之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:22.34,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呆呆地仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:25.72,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊啊 月色真美
